$ git init
$ touch sample
$ git add sample
$ git status
$ git commit
$ git commit -m initial commit
$ git config --global user.name Panthamajay
$ git config --global user.mail panthamajay11@gmail.com
$ git remote
$ git remote add origin
$ git push -u origin https://github.com/Panthamajay/sample.git 

 
These are the steps which I hve followed for creating a DVCS
